name: PassiveExpiringMap_keySetTest
description: Unit tests for the keySet functionality of PassiveExpiringMap, including scenarios with expired and non-expired entries.

test_cases.name: testKeySetWithExpiredEntries
test_cases.description: Tests the keySet functionality when all entries have expired.

test_cases.name: testKeySetWithoutExpiredEntries
test_cases.description: Tests the keySet functionality when no entries have expired.

test_cases.name: testKeySetAfterPartialExpiration
test_cases.description: Tests the keySet functionality after some entries have expired and new entries are added.

test_cases.name: testKeySetWithNeverExpiringEntries
test_cases.description: Tests the keySet functionality with entries that never expire.

test_cases.name: testKeySetWithZeroTimeToLive
test_cases.description: Tests the keySet functionality with entries that have zero time to live.
